data.description: Location! In sought after Poquoson. This home is the one you've been waiting for. This Custom Built home sits on almost one acre:  offers an Open Concept, chef style kitchen, gas cooking, quartz counter tops, large pantry, prep area, island, and beautiful cabinets with pull outs.  Designated laundry/mud room.  Very large FROG over garage is also considered the 4th bedroom.  All bedrooms are large in size.  Primary bedroom has 2 walk-in closets, and an en-suite with shower and jetted tub.  You will be wowed the moment you enter.  There is a private office downstairs, living room with gas fireplace, and formal dining area. Large lot offering plenty of room for entertaining, privacy, and allowing relaxation on the back screened porch.  Option to assume a 2.25% loan balance.
